snippet.title: Super Clash Bros - 2019 pre-alpha trailer
snippet.description:
More trailers/character reveals are coming! Subscribe and click that bell for notifications. 
You can also join the community on Discord: https://discord.gg/5fxwu9n

The 8-bit remix of the Smash Ultimate theme was made by Tater-Tot Tunes: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v4efe99x-4k
The Mega Man X remix of the theme was made by MyNewSoundtrack: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TFL6PHFzvUQ
